<%- include("partials/navbar.ejs") %>
<header class="bg-white shadow">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Posts</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
  <!-- First post -->
  <div class="ml-[40px] mt-[20px] border-r border-b border-l border-t border-gray-400 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal sm:m-5">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2 border-b-4 border-gray-800">The Rise of AI in Everyday Technology</div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
        Artificial Intelligence (AI) is no longer a futuristic concept; it's an integral part of our daily lives. From
        personalized recommendations on streaming platforms to voice assistants like Siri and Alexa, AI is
        revolutionizing how we interact with technology. It helps businesses automate processes, improves customer
        service with chatbots, and enhances data-driven decision-making. As AI continues to evolve, its impact will
        only grow, unlocking new opportunities for innovation and making technology more intuitive and accessible for
        everyone. Embracing AI will undoubtedly shape the future of how we live and work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Second post -->
  <div class="mr-[40px] mt-[20px] border-r border-b border-l border-t border-gray-400 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal sm:m-5">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2 border-b-4 border-gray-800">The Importance of Continuous Learning in Tech</div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
        In technology, staying updated is essential for success. New tools, languages, and frameworks are constantly
        emerging, and embracing continuous learning helps professionals stay ahead. Whether through online courses,
        tutorials, or community events like hackathons, ongoing education is key to adapting to industry changes. By
        learning new skills and exploring innovative solutions, tech professionals can enhance their problem-solving
        abilities and remain competitive in a fast-paced field. In tech, growth never stopsâ€”keep learning, and stay ahead!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Looping through subjects -->
  <% for (var i = 0; i < subject.length; i++) { %>
    <div class="mr-[40px] mt-[20px] border-r border-b border-l border-t border-gray-400 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal sm:m-5">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2 border-b-4 border-gray-800"><%= subject[i] %></div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-base"><%= body[i] %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% } %>

</div>

<%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

